<p><cs><mcol><col><b>Linnaean system</b></col>, <col><b>Linnean
system</b></col></mcol> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>, <cd>the system in which the
classes of plants are founded mainly upon the number of stamens, and the
orders upon the pistils; the artificial or sexual system.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

